\cs30\b\fs36\super \chftn {\footnote \pard\plain \s31\qj\fi567\sb40\sa40\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \f40\fs30\lang1036\cgrid {\cs30\b\fs36\super \chftn }{ Variante du manuscrit\~:
